sections.text: The Secretary of State is hereby authorized to distribute the laws and journals of the state.SourceLaws 1907, c. 78, § 1, p. 289;R.S.1913, § 3733;Laws 1915, c. 72, § 1, p. 185;C.S.1922, § 3126;C.S.1929, § 49-501;R.S.1943, § 49-501;Laws 1977, LB 3

49-501.Session laws and journals; distribution by Secretary of State.

The Secretary of State is hereby authorized to distribute the laws and journals of the state.

SourceLaws 1907, c. 78, § 1, p. 289;R.S.1913, § 3733;Laws 1915, c. 72, § 1, p. 185;C.S.1922, § 3126;C.S.1929, § 49-501;R.S.1943, § 49-501;Laws 1977, LB 3, § 1.
